<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kevin's Deck Boxes - Custom Handcrafted Wood Storage</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="nav-logo">
                <img src="images/image-removebg-preview.png" alt="Kevin's Deck Boxes Logo">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="home" class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h2>Handcrafted Wooden Deck Boxes</h2>
                <p>Custom-built storage for your Magic: The Gathering cards and more</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about" class="about">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h2>Custom Wood Deck Boxes</h2>
                <p>I'm Kevin. I build wooden deck boxes. Custom work, any wood you want.</p>
                
                <p>Need storage for your cards? I'll make it. Pick the wood, tell me the size, and I'll build it. Quality work that lasts.</p>

                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>Custom Work</h3>
                        <p>Made to order. Your wood choice, your dimensions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>Any Wood Type</h3>
                        <p>Oak, walnut, cherry, maple, mahogany - you name it.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>Built Right</h3>
                        <p>No shortcuts. Quality materials, solid construction.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>Fair Pricing</h3>
                        <p>Cost depends on wood type and labor. Honest quotes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="ideas" class="ideas">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h2>What I Build</h2>
                <p>Here are some common requests. If you have something else in mind, just ask.</p>

                <div class="ideas-list">
                    <div class="idea-item">
                        <h3>MTG Commander Boxes</h3>
                        <p>Single or double deck storage for 100-card Commander decks. Sleeved or unsleeved.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="idea-item">
                        <h3>Standard MTG Deck Boxes</h3>
                        <p>60-card deck storage. Single deck or multi-deck cases.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="idea-item">
                        <h3>Playing Card Storage</h3>
                        <p>Standard poker decks, bridge cards, collectible decks - any card game.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="idea-item">
                        <h3>Dice Boxes</h3>
                        <p>Storage for dice collections. Multiple compartments available.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="idea-item">
                        <h3>Custom Projects</h3>
                        <p>Got a different idea? Let's talk about it. Custom means custom.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="gallery" class="gallery">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h2>Past Work</h2>
                <p>Some boxes I've built.</p>

                <div class="gallery-grid">
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8b4513/ffffff?text=Walnut+Commander+Box" alt="Walnut Commander Box">
                        <p>Walnut Commander Box</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/d4a574/ffffff?text=Oak+Double+Deck" alt="Oak Double Deck Box">
                        <p>Oak Double Deck Box</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/654321/ffffff?text=Cherry+Dice+Box" alt="Cherry Dice Box">
                        <p>Cherry Dice Box</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/8b4513/ffffff?text=Mahogany+Standard" alt="Mahogany Standard Box">
                        <p>Mahogany Standard Box</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/d4a574/ffffff?text=Maple+Multi-Deck" alt="Maple Multi-Deck Box">
                        <p>Maple Multi-Deck Box</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/654321/ffffff?text=Custom+Gaming+Case" alt="Custom Gaming Case">
                        <p>Custom Gaming Case</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="process" class="process">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                
                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>1. Pick Your Wood</h3>
                    <p>Oak, walnut, cherry, maple, mahogany, or something else. Each has different grain and color. Tell me what you like.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>2. Size & Features</h3>
                    <p>How many decks? What size cards? Need compartments for dice or tokens? I'll build it to fit.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>3. Get A Quote</h3>
                    <p>Price depends on wood type and how much work it takes. I'll give you a straight answer on cost.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>4. I Build It</h3>
                    <p>Once we agree on details and price, I get to work. Quality takes time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="contact">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h2>Get Started</h2>
                <p>Call for an estimate. Tell me what you need, I'll tell you what it costs.</p>
                
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h3>Call For Quote</h3>
                    <p class="phone-number">ðŸ“ž (555) 123-4567</p>
                    <p>Straight answers on pricing and timeline.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="cta">
                    <p>Quality work. Fair prices. No nonsense.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Kevin's Deck Boxes. Handcrafted and Sculpted.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
